<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>śā</unclear>kābdē śararaṁ<unclear>dhra</unclear>nandagaṇitē śrībhīmanāthāya
<lb n="2"/>yā khyātā haihayavaṁśajasya mahiṣī śrīkīrttirājasya <unclear>sā</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādāddīpa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kamuttarāyaṇadinē dīpyaṁta<unclear>mā</unclear>tāraka<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> kīrttisvarggadhunīpavitri
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tamahī śrīrēkidēvyāhvayā [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] śakavarṣa 995 svasti sa<unclear>rvva</unclear>lōkāśraya<unclear>śrī</unclear>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>viṣṇuvarddhanamahārājula pravarddhamāna vijayarājyasaṁvatsara 13
<lb n="6"/>gunēṇṭi yuttarāyaṇanimittamuna rākudiri karttirāju peṇḍemu rēkama śrībhīmē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>śvaramahādēvaraku beṭṭina yakhaṇḍavartti lōhapu dhūpāra diviya yokkaṇṭi dīni
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ki nācaṁdrārkkamu neyi sariyiccuvārugānū gilaramuna cāmabōla veṁṭiyayu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁ gommabōla kāṭiyayu bādabhōla doḍḍanayuṁ gommakava talliyayu berasina bōlu
<lb n="10"/>nalvura vasamunā beṭṭina yeḍlu 50 divasapaḍi vōyaṁgala
<lb n="11"/>tribhuvanāṁkuśa nē māna 1 likitamu mārapāsāri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

